    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but isn't saying that \"multiculturalism\" is a standard for being \"healthy\" just a specific political viewpoint? it feels like you're basically saying that any nationalism that isn't inclusive is automatically \"extreme\" or \"hostile.\" can't a country be perfectly stable and successful just by prioritizing its own citizens and culture above everything else?",
